author: Home Repair Tutor
description: I'm installing Schluter DITRA Peel and Stick over concrete. Using PRIMER-PS can enhance the bond. I like this option because it's easy and fast to install. I use a float to activate the pressure-sensitive adhesive. Then I can immediately set tile over it. Many thanks to Schluter for sponsoring this tutorial #schlutersystems #tilefloor #homerenovation #sponsored
title: Schluter DITRA Peel and Stick Tips Over Concrete - #shorts #schlutersystems #sponsored
